          My approach is simple: <span class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white font-medium">quality isn't a phase — it's a culture</span>.
          I design test strategies from scratch, build scalable automation frameworks,
          and mentor teams to think quality-first. Whether it's a Web3 protocol or a
          B2B platform, I focus on real impact — fewer bugs in production, faster
          releases, and teams that own their quality.
        </p>
